Kaggle Learn Pandas exercise material

This repository contains a modified derivative of exercise notebooks from:
https://github.com/Kaggle/learntools

Source files:
notebooks/pandas/raw/ex_0.ipynb through ex_5.ipynb
Reference commit:
8a8d4450a699c864febc419fb27ec41443a5942b

Modifications:
- Combined six exercise notebooks into one notebook.
- Reorganized every exercise into problem, answer-input, and solution/explanation cells.
- Added Japanese summaries and code explanations.
- Removed learntools answer-checking calls from the standalone learning notebook.
- Removed file-reading and file-writing exercises.
- Replaced external datasets with deterministic DataFrames created inside the notebook.
- Added an executable final self-check.

